## Conventions
<!-- branch naming, error handling, logging, config, testing approach (TDD) -->
- Branch per story: `feat/<JIRA_KEY>-slug`
- Tests first (TDD): acceptance criteria → failing tests → implementation
- **Test layout mirrors the source tree:** `app/<module>/x.py` → `tests/unit/<module>/test_x.py`
  (and `tests/integration/<module>/…`). Test-type (unit/integration/e2e) at the top, module
  sub-folders under each. Never place tests flat in `tests/unit/`.
